= RF citizen science
With a lot of older radio technology getting much cheaper, it is now possible
for regular people to help in RF research. I think building tools and
technology to help armature scientist contribute data to projects would be very
useful. This project would be mostly about building aggregation tools and
hardware for SDR. This is partially based on Dr Schab's desktop radio project.

